 <span data-ttu-id="f6456-105">在<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded>以编程方式或鼠标指针进入单元<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>格的情况下检索属性值时, 也会发生此事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6456-105">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event also occurs whenever the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is retrieved, either programmatically or when the mouse pointer enters a cell.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f6456-106">您可以使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.ColumnIndex%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.RowIndex%2A>属性来确定单元的状态或值, 并使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellToolTipTextNeededEventArgs.ToolTipText%2A>此信息来设置属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6456-106">You can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.ColumnIndex%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.RowIndex%2A> properties to determine the state or value of a cell, and use this information to set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellToolTipTextNeededEventArgs.ToolTipText%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f6456-107">此属性将用单元<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A>属性的值进行初始化, 该属性的值将重写。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6456-107">This property is initialized with the value of the cell <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A> property, which the event value overrides.</span></span>  
  
